data.description: A charming older home that boasts both character and space. This spacious residence, set amidst a picturesque landscape, offers a unique opportunity for buyers seeking a timeless property. The standout feature of this house is the majestic front yard adorned with large, mature trees, providing a serene and welcoming atmosphere and a large back yard. The house, although older, exudes classic charm and potential. The living areas are adorned with period details, adding to the home's distinctive character. In addition to the inviting indoor space, the property's outdoor charm cannot be overlooked. The expansive front yard, graced by these magnificent mature trees, offers a beautiful and shady setting for outdoor relaxation, play, or gatherings. While the house may require some updates to modernize its amenities, its timeless appeal and the tranquil setting is hard to beat!
